OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775235955
OL,3,CHumane badger traps to be deployed in
OL,4,Csearch for Samba the missing capybara
OL,6,FTeams searching for the missing
OL,7,Fcapybara from Marwell Zoo say they've
OL,8,Fgot humane badger traps ready to
OL,9,Fdeploy once the search narrows.
OL,11,FSamba has been missing for more than
OL,12,Ftwo weeks after escaping from the
OL,13,FHampshire park.
OL,15,FThe mischievous animal had only
OL,16,Farrived at Marwell, along with another
OL,17,Ffemale capybara, named Tango, on
OL,18,FMonday 16 March from Jimmy's Farm &
OL,19,FWildlife Park, in Suffolk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
