CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775235955
OL,3,CHumane badger traps to be deployed in
OL,4,Csearch for Samba the missing capybara
OL,6,FSamba and Tango were being held in a
OL,7,Ftemporary holding area, where they
OL,8,Fboth managed to escape the following
OL,9,Fday.
OL,11,FZookeepers were able to quickly locate
OL,12,Fand retrieve Tango, but Samba evaded
OL,13,Fcapture.
OL,15,FShe was last seen near the River
OL,16,FItchen on 22 March.
OL,18,FSince Samba escaped teams from Marwell
OL,19,Fhave used drones, thermal imaging and
OL,20,Fa 24/7 hotline in the search.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
