PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775235955
OL,3,CHumane badger traps to be deployed in
OL,4,Csearch for Samba the missing capybara
OL,6,FA spokesperson from Marwell said: "Our
OL,7,Fcontinued message to the public is
OL,8,Fthat if they are in the local area and
OL,9,Fspot Samba to make sure they:
OL,11,F"We continue to work with a specialist
OL,12,Fdog unit who is tracing her scent,
OL,13,Fthermal drones and camera traps to
OL,14,Fnarrow down the search area.
OL,16,F"We have humane badger traps on
OL,17,Fstandby as well, which we'll deploy
OL,18,Fonce a narrower search area is
OL,19,Fidentified and our team is on 24/7
OL,20,Falert to go in and retrieve her."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
